\": 650, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day you want me to retire every day guys.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You ask me for that every single day.\\\"\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 22-time Grand Slam champion could not give a real answer about his career expiry date, he shed light on when he might consider quitting.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 22-time Grand Slam champion\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"a real answer\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"his career expiry date\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I am trying to do my best every single day.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I answer but I cannot live every single day with the feeling that it's going to be or not going to be my last match.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"my last match\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I come here, I try my best, I play and when I decide to stop playing or when I decide to keep going, I will let you know.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, I just try my best every single day, trying to enjoy a thing that I have been enjoying for so much time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"so much time\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Long-standing WTA event scrapped and worries raised that more will follow Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and ou